cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper proposes a probabilistic framework for reinforcement learning that incorporates prior knowledge, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also applies the framework to navigation tasks, which are often studied in robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper mentions using the framework with entropy-regularized RL, which is a technique commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
